1) Raleigh Road Elementary School is located less than 1 mile from
the studied intersection and was in session on the date of the
count, as were all Cumberland County Schools.
3) EB approach grade is 0%, SB is -1%, and NB is +1%.
4) Area lighting was not present at the count location.
5) No highway construction was observed that impacted normal
6) Data collection equipment was operating correctly at time of
7) Counter took breaks from 9:00 – 9:15 AM, 1:15 – 1:30 PM and
3:30 – 4:00 PM. Data for these periods was interpolated.
8) Counter Notes: Vehicles turning in and out of the Marathon Gas Station via the Ramsey Street driveway
were counted on BANK 1. All vehicles entering and exiting the study area intersection were counted on the
standard turning movement buttons and are accounted for in the “All Vehicles” summary attached.
